reviews.name: Mani Subhash
reviews.text:
Let me say this - am pleasantly surprised to see a property of such good standards in a not so big and hustling place like Bhadrachalam. This stay has everything a family needs for a comfortable stay - fully furnished, spring mattresses, exotic toiletries, spacious and close proximity to temple. Host Vihar has shown exceptional hospitality, he treated us as his own family. He was so courteous to respond to our queries before visiting and helping us with updates on flood conditions prevailing owed to torrential rains. After reaching, he did everything to ensure we all are comfortable, including suggesting us to check out late if needed and treat the place as our own.

Unmatched hospitality with modern amenities is what you can expect here. So grateful for letting us stay in this beautiful place.
